value.string: Truly a dream! This elegant two bedroom, two bath condo is fully furnished in Tommy Bahama Style decor. Located on the top of the property, it has lovely cross breezes. Workout gym and newly remodeled pool area are a few of the amenities that add to this properties appeal. Walking distance to Wailea's finest restaurants and the Shops at Wailea. Must see to appreciate!

This beautiful 2nd story end unit offers vaulted ceilings and extra windows making it feel much larger than it is. It is in excellent condition, secluded location in the complex, and is offered fully furnished - turn key. Features of Unit U-201 include 2 split system A/C units, granite counter tops, and washer/dryer. The lovely amenities include club house, gym, pool, spa and kitchen/bbq facilities. Easy to show.

This beautiful one-bedroom, two-bath unit is in the highly sought after oceanfront condominium complex of Wailea Ekahi. Inside there is a double door that divides the living room and one bath from the master suite, which means this unit can also work well for four people. Nicely furnished with updated bathrooms and kitchen. The large lanai off the master bedroom could be enclosed for additional living area. There are two split AC’s in the unit to keep it cool and quiet. This property has FOUR swimming pools, TWO paddle tennis courts and a beach pavilion that can be reserved for entertaining. Golf membership at all three fabulous Wailea golf courses is available for owners of Wailea Ekahi. Enjoy all the amenities and privileges that Wailea offers!
